import Button from "@material-ui/core/Button";
import Container from "@material-ui/core/Container";
import Grid from "@material-ui/core/Grid";
import TextField from "@material-ui/core/TextField";
import { makeStyles } from "@material-ui/core/styles";
import { Link } from "react-router-dom";

const useStyles = makeStyles((theme) => ({
  container: {
    padding: theme.spacing(3),
    position: "absolute",
    top: "50%",
    left: "50%",
    transform: "translate(-50%, -50%)",
  },
}));

export default function AddResource() {
  const classes = useStyles();

  function handleSubmit(e) {
    console.log(e.target.value)
  }

  return (
    <Container className={classes.container} maxWidth="xs">
      <form>
        <Grid container spacing={3}>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <Grid container spacing={2}>
              <Grid item xs={12}>
                <TextField
                  fullWidth
                  label="Source"
                  name="source"
                  size="small"
                  variant="outlined"
                  required={true}
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={12}>
                <TextField
                  fullWidth
                  label="Funding Name"
                  name="funding_name"
                  size="small"
                  variant="outlined"
                  required={true}
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={12}>
                <TextField
                  fullWidth
                  label="Description"
                  name="decription"
                  size="medium"
                  variant="outlined"
                  required={true}
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={12}>
                <TextField
                  fullWidth
                  label="Amount"
                  name="amount"
                  size="small"
                  variant="outlined"
                  required={false}
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={12}>
                <TextField
                  fullWidth
                  label="Contact Person"
                  name="contact_person"
                  size="small"
                  variant="outlined"
                  required={true}
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={12}>
                <TextField
                  fullWidth
                  label="Website Address"
                  name="web"
                  size="small"
                  variant="outlined"
                  required={false}
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={12}>
                <TextField
                  fullWidth
                  label="Eligible"
                  name="eligible"
                  size="small"
                  variant="outlined"
                  required={false}
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={12}>
                <TextField
                  fullWidth
                  label="Deadline"
                  name="deadline"
                  size="small"
                  variant="outlined"
                  required={false}
                />
              </Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <Button
              color="secondary"
              fullWidth
              type="submit"
              variant="contained"
              onClick = {handleSubmit}
            >
              Submit
            </Button>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </form>
    </Container>
  );
}
